Description: KDE - Experimental new desktop metaphor
DescDetail: <<
CardDesk is a plugin system that is eventually meant to
to augment KDE's interface with "cards", self-contained
movable plugin containers.

Slicker is a replacement for the KDE kicker taskbar system
that uses CardDesk.
